\f0\fs32\b WCMICS UML Class Diagram\par
\fs22\b0 Based on classes found under main.app, main.ui, main.service, main.dao, main.model, and main.database in the current WCMICS project.\par
The diagram is split into three focused UML views so the system stays readable inside one document.\par
\par
\b Legend:\b0  *-- composition   o-- aggregation   --> association/use   ..> dependency\par
\par
\b 1. Application Flow View\b0\par
\f1\fs18
+----------------------+     *--     +----------------------+\par
| MainFrame            |------------>| AppRouter            |\par
| - root : JPanel      |             | - container : JPanel |\par
| - layout : CardLayout|             | - layout : CardLayout|\par
| - auth : AuthService |             | + register(name,view)|\par
| + setupRoutes()      |             | + navigate(route)    |\par
| + main()             |             +----------+-----------+\par
+----------+-----------+                        ^\par
           | registers                          |\par
           |                                    |\par
           +--> WelcomePage                     |\par
           +--> LoginPanel .......... uses .....+\par
           +--> SignupPanel ......... uses .....+\par
           +--> Menro\par
           +--> Barangay\par
\par
+----------------------+     ..>     +----------------------+\par
| LoginPanel           |------------>| UserSession          |\par
| + performLogin()     |             | <<static>>           |\par
|                      |             | + startSession()     |\par
|                      |             | + logout()           |\par
+----------+-----------+             +----------------------+\par
           |\par
           | uses\par
           v\par
+----------------------+     -->     +----------------------+\par
| AuthService          |------------>| AccountDao           |\par
| - dao : AccountDao   |             | - conn : Connection  |\par
| + login()            |             | + findByEmail()      |\par
| + register()         |             | + findById()         |\par
| + changePassword()   |             | + updateLastLogin()  |\par
+----------------------+             +----------+-----------+\par
                                                |\par
                                                v\par
                                         +------------------+\par
                                         | Account          |\par
                                         | accountId        |\par
                                         | name, email      |\par
                                         | role, status     |\par
                                         | barangayId       |\par
                                         +------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+     o--     +----------------------+\par
| Menro                |------------>| Sidebar              |\par
| + main()             |             | + actionPerformed()  |\par
+----------+-----------+             +----------+-----------+\par
           | *-- admin.HomePanel                |\par
           | *-- SchedulePanel                  | --> AppRouter\par
           | *-- ManagementPanel                |\par
           | *-- admin.BarangayPanel            v\par
           | *-- UsersPanel              +----------------------+\par
           | *-- admin.SettingsPanel     | Header               |\par
           |                              | ..> HeaderService    |\par
           |                              | ..> UserSession      |\par
           |                              +----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+     o--     +----------------------+\par
| Barangay             |------------>| Sidebar              |\par
| + main()             |             +----------------------+\par
+----------+-----------+\par
           | *-- officials.HomePanel\par
           | *-- ReportsPanel\par
           | *-- officials.SettingsPanel\par
           v\par
     +----------------------+\par
     | Header               |\par
     +----------------------+\par
\f0\fs22\par
Notes:\par
- MainFrame boots authentication, registers the welcome/login/signup routes, and opens Menro or Barangay based on Account.role.\par
- LoginPanel updates UserSession after a successful AuthService.login call.\par
- Shared UI building blocks are AppRouter, Sidebar, and Header.\par
- Key panel-service links in the MENRO dashboard are: admin.HomePanel ..> HomeService and ScheduleService, SchedulePanel ..> ScheduleService, ManagementPanel ..> PersonnelService, TeamService, and TruckService, admin.BarangayPanel ..> ReportService, ComplaintService, and RequestService, UsersPanel ..> AccountDao, and admin.SettingsPanel ..> AccountDao, AuthService, and UserSession.\par
\page
\b 2. Service And DAO View\b0\par
\f1\fs18
+----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+\par
| AuthService          |---------->| AccountDao           |---------->| Account              |\par
| BarangayService      |---------->| BarangayDao          |---------->| Barangay             |\par
| PersonnelService     |---------->| PersonnelDao         |---------->| Personnel            |\par
| TeamService          |---------->| TeamDao              |---------->| Team                 |\par
| TruckService         |---------->| TruckDao             |---------->| Truck                |\par
| ScheduleService      |---------->| ScheduleDao          |---------->| Schedule             |\par
| ReportService        |---------->| ReportDao            |---------->| Report               |\par
| ComplaintService     |---------->| ComplaintDao         |---------->| Complaint            |\par
| RequestService       |---------->| RequestDao           |---------->| Request              |\par
+----------------------+           +----------------------+           +----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+\par
| HomeService          |---------->| HomeDao              |---------->| HomeCardData         |\par
+----------------------+           +----------------------+           +----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+    -->    +----------------------+\par
| HeaderService        |---------->| NotificationDao      |---------->| NotificationSummary  |\par
| + build...Items()    |           | + fetchSummary()     |           +----------------------+\par
| ..> PopupItem        |           +----------------------+\par
+----------------------+\par
\par
SQLConnection ..> AccountDao, BarangayDao, PersonnelDao, TeamDao, TruckDao,\par
                 ScheduleDao, ReportDao, ComplaintDao, RequestDao,\par
                 HomeDao, NotificationDao\par
\par
DbSchemaHelper ..> AccountDao, TeamDao, NotificationDao\par
\f0\fs22\par
Notes:\par
- Most services are thin business wrappers around one DAO and one main model class.\par
- TeamDao is the richest DAO because it synchronizes team, truck, and personnel assignments.\par
- ScheduleDao joins barangay, barangay_admin, team, and schedule data into one Schedule view model.\par
- HeaderService builds PopupItem collections for the shared Header notification and account menus.\par
\page
\b 3. Core Domain View\b0\par
\f1\fs18
+----------------------+   0..* assignedTo   0..1   +----------------------+\par
| Account              |--------------------------->| Barangay             |\par
| accountId            |                            | barangayId           |\par
| name                 |                            | barangayName         |\par
| email                |                            | collectionDay        |\par
| role                 |                            | contact              |\par
| status               |                            +----------------------+\par
+----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+   1 leader          1      +----------------------+\par
| Team                 |--------------------------->| Personnel            |\par
| id                   |   0..1 driver       1      | id                   |\par
| teamName             |--------------------------->| fullName             |\par
| leaderId             |   0..* collectors   1      | role                 |\par
| driverId             |--------------------------->| status               |\par
| truckId              |                            | team                 |\par
| collectorIds [*]     |                            +----------------------+\par
+----------+-----------+\par
           |\par
           | 0..1 assignedTruck\par
           v\par
     +----------------------+\par
     | Truck                |\par
     | id                   |\par
     | plateNumber          |\par
     | truckType            |\par
     | status               |\par
     | assignedTeam         |\par
     +----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+   1 collectionFor   1      +----------------------+\par
| Schedule             |--------------------------->| Barangay             |\par
| id                   |   0..1 servedBy     1      +----------------------+\par
| barangayName         |--------------------------->| Team                 |\par
| collectorTeam        |                            +----------------------+\par
| date                 |\par
| time                 |\par
| status               |\par
+----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+   0..* filedFor     1      +----------------------+\par
| Report               |--------------------------->| Barangay             |\par
| reportId             |                            +----------------------+\par
| barangayId           |\par
| status               |\par
| isRead               |\par
| createdAt            |\par
+----------------------+\par
\par
+----------------------+          +----------------------+\par
| Complaint            |          | Request              |\par
| complaintId          |          | requestId            |\par
| message              |          | message              |\par
| location             |          | location             |\par
| status               |          | status               |\par
| isRead               |          | isRead               |\par
+----------------------+          +----------------------+\par
\par
HomeCardData ..> derived from Schedule and Complaint counts\par
NotificationSummary ..> derived from Barangay, Schedule, and Report counts\par
\f0\fs22\par
Notes:\par
- Team is the central operational entity because it binds personnel roles and one truck.\par
- Schedule represents a joined planning view rather than a fully normalized entity with foreign-key fields inside the model class.\par
- Complaint and Request currently store location as text, while Report is directly linked to Barangay through barangayId.\par
\par
\b End of document\b0\par
